Title: Representations of q-Minkowski space algebra

Comments: 12 pages

Journal-ref: Alg.Anal. 6 (1994) 195-205; St.Petersburg Math.J. 6 (1995) 365-374

The properties of the quantum Minkowski space algebra are discussed. Itsirreducible representations with highest weight vectors are constructed andare pointed out.